Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Matsunaga, čo si robil cez prestávku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Poď s nami niekedy na karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Mattsun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} To bolelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Našiel som ju! Našiel som ju!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Našiel si koho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Santu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Mattsun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Vravím ti, je to pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Oh, Natchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ah! Kei{\i1}-chan{\i0}, počúvaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Si akýsi čulý, na začiatok semestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Lebo cez vianoce som stretol Santu hej?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Jasné, jasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ona študuje na tejto škole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} A má šál!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Vravíš moc nahlas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Je to šál, ktorý som chcel dať svojej ex, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ale dal som ho jej, lebo jej bola zima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Používaj svoj vnútorný hlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Chcel som sa vás spýtať, ako sa mám k nej dostať?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44\pos(634,578)\b1}Dobré ráno
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44\pos(634,578)\b1}Prečo vyťahuješ svoj bič?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44\pos(634,578)\b1}My ideme spievať.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44\b1\pos(651,579)}Aj tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44\b1\pos(651,579)}Dôvody?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44\b1\pos(651,579)}Aké dôvody?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} O čom sa rozprávajú?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Sklapni.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Takže takto si ju stretol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Mohol si ju teda pozvať von už vtedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ale ti vreckovky, čo mi dala boli z karaoke štúdia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Mala ich ako reklamu na karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Takže si ťa možno ani nepamätá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ale nosí ten šál, ktorý jej dal podivín ako ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Myslím si, že je to možné, vieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Čo je možné?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Niečo ako osud, vieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Dala mi vreckovky, keď som potreboval a ona používa šál, čo som jej dal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ah, a je v dievčenskom móde.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Nie, len si predstavuje to, čo chce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Bludy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Dobre, tu pomôže iba...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Povedz mi, keď ju uvidíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Začnem rozhovor a spravím ti vhodné podmienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Fakt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Čo jej povieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Takže...Začnem s...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Si fakt roztomilá, vieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ty si hovado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Hashiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Čau, brácho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Hovor mi {\i1}učiteľ{\i0}, keď sme v škole, Katakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Hashiba, dneska máš službu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Potrebujem s niečím pomôcť. Môžeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Oh...uh...Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Len ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ak chceš, tak si zavolaj niekoho ďalšieho na pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Hej, mohol by jeden z vás...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44\b1}Práci zdar!\NPráci zdar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Bezcitní hlupáci.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Vy štyria ste si vždy boli takí blízki,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}ale to, ako ste každý ľahostajní k druhému je niekedy smiešne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}To nieje smiešne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Všetci sú takí chladní!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Aj Keiichi? No, je to druhý syn, nakoniec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Učiteľ, vy poznáte každého študenta na škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Hm? Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Niekoho hľadám.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Dievča, so stredne dlhými vlasmi, jemne hnedými.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Vyzerala ako tichší typ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Oh, a myslím, že brigáduje v karaoke štúdiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Hmm...Napadá mi veľa takých dievčat, ktoré by pasovali do tvojho opisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Učiteľ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Už si sa prebrala?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Je ti lepšie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} To je ona!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Prečo spala?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Prečo tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Whoa, opatrne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Stále máš závraty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Je tu ešte niekto ďalší, takže sa obleč. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Dobre, učiteľ, ja už idem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Buď opatrná.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Učiteľ, kto to bol?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Oh, to bola Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Raz za čas sem príde. Má na to dôvody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ale nechcem, aby si ktokoľvek myslel, že s ňou zaobchádzam lepšie, ako s ostatnými.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Hashiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Necháš si to pre seba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Samozrejme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ona je chalan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}A je učiteľova?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Prečo by inak spala v kabinete?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Nad čím rozmýšľaš? Nad mladším bratom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Moj brat toho o sebe moc nenahovorí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Natchan, máš rád tú Kobayakawu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Máš o ňu len záujem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Alebo ju miluješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Keď sa tak pýtaš...Myslím, že ma iba zaujíma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ale trochu ma to zarazilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ak si si neni istý, tak sa tým netráp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Neviem, tak budem spievať.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Spievaj! Spievaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Prepáčte za vyrušenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Doniesla som vám vaše nápoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Kto chcel kofolu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Oh, ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}A komu mám dať ľadovú kávu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Sem, mne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Oh, ty si ten z minula.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Áno, som Hashiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Hashiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Prosím, relaxujte a užívajte si.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Uh...Dobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} To bolo to  dievča, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Milujem ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Len z tohoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Celý čas bola úplne bez výrazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Som neskutočne šťastný z toho, že si ma pamätá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Taktiež, je vzácne pre niekoho, kto pracuje v obsluhe, aby sa neusmievala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Teraz chcem vidieť jej úsmev ešte viac!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Aha, V podstate, chceš vidieť jej tvár, keď nebude ponížená.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Alebo skrivenú bolesťou, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Prišiel som na to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Hm,  nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Teraz si objednám ďalší pohár a budem dúfať, že príde zase Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Zdravím.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Nakoniec už neprišla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Žiješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Nemyslíš, že si toho vypil trochu moc?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Idem na záchod.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Idem na to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Pomôž jej, ak si chlap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Do toho, Natchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ale ako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Sprav hocičo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Jednoducho niečo sprav!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Do toho, Natchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ukáž jej, aký si cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Urob niečo. Urob niečo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Prestaňte obťažovať moje dievča!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Áno? Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Toto je ten moment, kedy sa treba otočiť a bežať?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Áno. Bežme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Uh, nie, nechápeš situáciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Vyzerá to tak, že títo gentlemani nevedia po Japonsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Čo?\NČo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} He?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Blbé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Dobre, idem tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Žiješ ešte?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}V pohode?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Čaute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ona je moja, jasné?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Vravím ti, ruky preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Oh, Natchan, nazdar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Predvčerom bola riadna sranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Bol si najlepší, Natchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Chalani...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Ste takí zákerní!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Čo? Ty plačeš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Uh, prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Bolo to také smiešne, že sme si nemohli pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Som vážne v šoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Dobre, chápeme, vysmrkaj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Daj si žuvačku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Natchan, bude to v pohode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Každý zlyhá aspoň raz za život.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Tsuyopon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Mimochodom, netrápi ťa viac jej vzťah s učiteľom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Teraz nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Na to už pravepodobne dávno zabudol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Natchan je obalený temnotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Naoe, zbieram zošity z matematiky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Potom pošlem Natchana, nech svoj zanesie sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Som si viac ako istý, že nemám šťastie na dievčatá a že sa nehodím na romantiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}A nikdy nezanesú môj zošit za mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44} Vchádzam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Zabudol som dať svoj zošit predtým, tak som ho doniesol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Nieje tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs44}Učiteľ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
